[576.897474, "o", "# Directory$\r\n$\r\nDirectory is a small menu-driven contacts program.$\r\n$\r\nThis task includes the original challenge binary and source for local analysis:$\r\n$\r\n- `directory`$\r\n- `directory.c`$\r\n$\r\nThe program stores up to 10 names in fixed-size stack slots.$\r\n"]
